Program: Outlook
Title: 03/08/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00j543p
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 4 Aug 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, why the smartest streets in Tel Aviv have been invaded by a sea of pop up tents. The woman imprisoned as a teenager tells us how she survived 28 years in a North Korean labour camp and the British student Mary-Jess Leaverland on how she sang her way to stardom in China. Show less